fields.title: Getting Started with Django
fields.body: Learn how to set up your first Django project, configure the database, and run the development server.

fields.title: Django Models Deep Dive
fields.body: Explore Django models in depth, including fields, relationships, and custom managers.

fields.title: Class-Based Views in Django
fields.body: Learn how to use Django's powerful class-based views to structure your application logically.

fields.title: Creating Reusable Django Apps
fields.body: Structure your project into decoupled apps to enable reuse and maintainability.

fields.title: Django Admin Customization
fields.body: Learn how to customize the Django admin to improve content management for your site.

fields.title: Django and Bootstrap 5 Integration
fields.body: Style your Django templates using Bootstrap 5 to create responsive and modern UIs.

fields.title: Deploying Django with Gunicorn and Nginx
fields.body: Step-by-step guide to deploy your Django project on a production server using Gunicorn and Nginx.

fields.body: Use signals to decouple logic in your Django app, such as post-save and pre-delete hooks.

fields.title: Working with Django REST Framework
fields.body: Learn the basics of Django REST Framework and how to build a RESTful API with Django.
